Package gov.ca.water.calgui.bus_service

In this package we have the business services like Dynamic control, Monitor, Table etc..

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDSSGrabber1Svc  
    IDynamicControlSvc
    This is the interface for applying the dynamic controls like enabling, disabling etc.
    IModelRunSvc
    This is the interface for Batch Run.
    IMonitorSvc
    This is the interface for Monitor the process which is done behind the seen.
    IScenarioSvc
    This is the interface for handling the cls file and run directory for CalLite scenarios.
    ISeedDataSvc
    This is the interface for loading the GUI_Link2.table and GUI_Link4.table.
    ITableSvc
    This is the interface that handles all the tables like gui_xchanneldays.table, gui_EiRatio.table etc.
    IXMLParsingSvc
    This is the interface for parsing the GUI.xml into SwingEngine.
